    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just a mistake though. it’s like the foundation is completely gone. i looked in the mirror and didn't even recognize myself. the version of me that people loved is dead, so i don't see the point in trying to build something new. if that person is gone, then what's even left to save?",
